    <!-- Invalidation -->
    <h2>The Invalidation Discipline</h2>
    <div class="invalidation-box">
        <h3>How It Works</h3>
        <p>Every piece of analysis we publish includes explicit invalidation criteria. Bull case triggers define what would end a bearish thesis. Bear case triggers define what would end a bullish one. We specify the indicators, the thresholds, and the timeframes. When the data fires, we act. This is not a discretionary overlay. It is the core of the process. We are not in the business of being right. We are in the business of understanding probabilities, positioning accordingly, and adjusting when the data tells us to.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- What We Deliver -->
    <h2>What We Deliver</h2>
    <p><span class="emphasis">Published Research:</span> Currently publishing the 12-part Diagnostic Dozen educational series (free on Substack), plus regular long-form macro analysis, single-chart insights, periodic chartbooks (50-75 charts), and forward outlooks. All research is built on the proprietary framework, not recycled consensus.</p>
    <p><span class="emphasis">Advisory &amp; Institutional:</span> Direct strategist access, bespoke research, model portfolio guidance, investment committee participation, and fractional CIO engagements. Tailored to the client's needs, from research-only subscriptions to embedded strategic partnerships.</p>

